<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>THE LAUGHING SOCK - <%= sock.name %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/show.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <% include ../partials/nav.ejs %>
    <% include ../partials/header.ejs %>
    <div class = "container">
      <div class = "productBox">
        <h2>"<%= sock.name %>"</h2>
        <img src = "<%= sock.img %>"/>
        <p>
          "<%= sock.description %>"
        </p>
        <% if (sock.qty > 0) { %>
          <li>
            Only <strong><%= sock.qty %></strong> left in stock!
          </li>
        <% } else { %>
          <li>
            <strong>
              OUT OF STOCK
            </strong>
          </li>
        <% } %>
        <% if (currentUser) { %>
        <a href = "<%= sock.id %>/edit">
          <button>
            EDIT
          </button>
        </a>
        <form action="/<%= sock.id %>?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
          <input type="submit" value="REMOVE">
        </form>
        <% } %>

        <!-- add an add to cart button that pushes to a cart array??? -->
        <form action="/<%= sock.id %>/cart?_method=PUT" method="POST">
          <input type="submit" value="ADD TO CART"/>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class = "reviews">
        <div class = "review">
          <h5>★★★★★</h5>
          <h6>loonyl0vegood</h6>
          <p>The socks are great! They're the best to eat pudding 🍮 in!</p>
        </div>
        <br/>
        <div class = "review">
          <h5>★★★☆☆</h5>
          <h6>chosen0ne</h6>
          <p>Wish I could give a good review like Luna's... but these just make my ⚡ hurt.</p>
        </div>
        <br/>
        <div class = "review">
          <h5>★☆☆☆☆</h5>
          <h6>thegingerfriend</h6>
          <p>I wish I could blame Hermione's cat for this, but my rat Scabbers chewed these up. 🙄</p>
        </div>
        <br/>
        <div class = "review">
          <h5>★★★★☆</h5>
          <h6>brightest_witch</h6>
          <p>These socks are almost as good as a 🐱 curled up at your feet, honestly. A match made in heaven for a bookworm like me!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
